snippet.title: Recast Amber Heard With Emilia Clarke?
snippet.description:
A new petition is calling for not only the replacement of Amber Heard in the upcoming Aquaman sequel, it's also got a suggestion for who the replacement should be. Who do you think should replace Amber Heard? Should she keep her role? Should she be cut from the film all together and not replaced? #amberheard #emiliaclarke #auqaman2
